 259:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      When The compilation define USE_HAL_OSPI_REGISTER_CALLBACKS is set to 0 or
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccbvotQ9.s 			page 6


 260:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      not defined, the callback registering feature is not available
